  "author": "XO_OX Designs",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "Boutique Chain showcase emphasizing Dissolving Archive. OBLONG's filter-heavy character produces strong, well-defined spectral events. Dissolving Archive with Chance 0.22 (more generous memory) and Dissolve 0.62 (faster decay) means past OBLONG phrases reappear frequently but decay quickly — they are present as brief ghosts rather than long memories. GrainMix 0.65 granulates the memory material heavily. ReverbMix 0.35 adds a small reverb to the grain output. The effect is an OBLONG that plays with echoes of itself at varying states of decomposition. Submerged mood — the archive is underwater, and memories have been through a depth transformation.",
